### ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing
### Errors when placing an entity and being too far
- Ensure you are close enough to the target position before attempting to place an entity. The maximum placement distance is 10 tiles.
### Errors when inspecting inventory
- When inspecting the inventory of an entity, ensure that the entity is not nil.
